title: Miss Hannah Minx ~Sekai ga Hannou~
overview: This popular series has been viewed over 42 million times worldwide on YouTube! Miss Hannah Minx, who continues to charm people all over the world with her beauty and clear eyes, has finally made her debut in Japan! She herself loves Japanese anime! In this video, she generously shows off cosplay outfits that are familiar to everyone! This exclusive DVD video, which you can never see on YouTube, allows you to fully enjoy Miss Hannah Minx, who has charmed the whole world!
